g 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Happy-Mondays-and-Rowetta-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Happy-Mondays-and-Rowetta-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Happy-Mondays-and-Rowetta-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Happy-Mondays-and-Rowetta-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/Happy-Mondays">Happy Mondays</a>宣布与歌手兼打击乐手<a href="/artists/Rowetta">Rowetta</a>分手 34 年后。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/happy-mondays-interview-mtv-emas-manchester-shaun-ryder-bez-biopic-new-album-tour-3812024">周一快乐，了解肖恩·莱德传记片的命运并在 2025 年“回归”</a><br /></strong></li></ul><p>今天（12月23日）在社交媒体上，歌手和周一快乐的周一都分享了罗塔（Rowetta）离开小组的声明。它写道：“星期一快乐和罗塔（Rowetta）宣布，罗塔（Rowetta）将不再与乐队一起表演。”</p><p>它继续说：“星期一快乐感谢Rowetta的服务，并祝她将来一切顺利。”这位歌手于1990年加入了乐队，并在乐队的单曲“ Step On”中出演，该乐队在排行榜上排名第五。她继续出现在他们的第三张和第四张录音室专辑《&#39;n&#39;n&#39;&#39;thrills and lallyaches&#39;和&#39;yes！&#39;，并加入乐队进行三场世界巡回演出。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DD7BesWtSKV/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; h