从“鳄鱼邓迪”（Crocodile Dundee）中的鳄鱼炸了，享年90岁https://www.nme.com/news/film/burt-the-crocodile-from-crocodile-dundee-has-died-age-90-3824515?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=burt-the-crocodile-from-鳄鱼dundee-has-died-age-90Aneesa Ahmed Mon, 23 Dec 2024 15:13:17 +0000 Film NewsNewsAustralia https://www.nme.com/?p=3824515 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Paul-Hogan-in-Crocodile-Dundee.-Credit_-Paramount-Pictures-min.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="保罗·霍根（Paul Hogan）在鳄鱼邓迪（Crocodile Dundee）。图片来源：派拉蒙影业" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Paul-Hogan-in-Crocodile-Dundee.-Credit_-Paramount-Pictures-min.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Paul-Hogan-in-Crocodile-Dundee.-Credit_-Paramount-Pictures-min-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Paul-Hogan-in-Crocodile-Dundee.-Credit_-Paramount-Pictures-min-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Paul-Hogan-in-Crocodile-Dundee.-Credit_-Paramount-Pictures-min-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Paul-Hogan-in-Crocodile-Dundee.-Credit_-Paramount-Pictures-min-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Paul-Hogan-in-Crocodile-Dundee.-Credit_-Paramount-Pictures-min-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “伯特确实是独一无二的。他不仅仅是一条鳄鱼；他是一种自然力量，提醒人们这些令人难以置信的生物的力量和威严。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/burt-the-crocodile-from-crocodile-dundee-has-died-age-90-3824515">“鳄鱼邓迪”（Crocodile Dundee）的鳄鱼布住了鳄鱼，死于</a><a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> ，现年90岁。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Paul-Hogan-in-Crocodile-Dundee.-Credit_-Paramount-Pictures-min.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="保罗·霍根（Paul Hogan）在鳄鱼邓迪（Crocodile Dundee）。图片来源：派拉蒙影业" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Paul-Hogan-in-Crocodile-Dundee.-Credit_-Paramount-Pictures-min.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Paul-Hogan-in-Crocodile-Dundee.-Credit_-Paramount-Pictures-min-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Paul-Hogan-in-Crocodile-Dundee.-Credit_-Paramount-Pictures-min-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Paul-Hogan-in-Crocodile-Dundee.-Credit_-Paramount-Pictures-min-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Paul-Hogan-in-Crocodile-Dundee.-Credit_-Paramount-Pictures-min-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Paul-Hogan-in-Crocodile-Dundee.-Credit_-Paramount-Pictures-min-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>鳄鱼伯特（Burt the Crocodile）在1986年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/australia">澳大利亚</a>喜剧<em>鳄鱼邓迪（Crocodile Dundee）</em>上与保罗·霍根（Paul Hogan）一起出演，享年90岁。</p><p>该消息得到了澳大利亚达尔文的水族馆和展览Crocosaurus Cove的证实，伯特自2008年以来一直居住，成为鳄鱼教育的“大使”。</p><p> Crocosaurus Cove在<a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DD5hifoSWYj/?hl=en&amp;img_index=2" target="_blank" rel="noopener">社交媒体</a>上写道：“伯特（Burt）在周末和平过世，估计已有90年的历史，这是一个令人难以置信的时代的终结。”</p><p> “伯特的人生故事是力量，韧性和人格，就像顶端本身一样大胆。伯特（Burt）在1980年代被俘虏在雷诺兹河（Reynolds River），成为世界上最受认可的鳄鱼之一，出现在<em>鳄鱼邓迪（Dundee）</em>中，并帮助将澳大利亚的形象塑造成坚固的自然美景和令人振奋的野生动植物的土地。”</p><p>后来读到：“伯特确实是其中一种。他不仅仅是一条鳄鱼；他是一条鳄鱼。他是自然的力量，提醒人们这些令人难以置信的生物的力量和威严。虽然他的性格可能具有挑战性，但这也让他如此令人难忘，深受与他共事的人和多年来拜访他的数千人的喜爱。来自世界各地的游客惊叹于他令人印象深刻的规模和指挥官，尤其是在喂食时。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DD5hifoSWYj/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><di